      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Endpoint\nGET /Tasks\nPOST /Tasks\n\n2. Input (Hva klient må sende):\nPOST /Tasks\n\n{\n    \"title\": \"Wash the car\"\n}\n\n3. Output (Hva serveren returnerer):\n{\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"title\": \"Wash the car\"\n    \"Completed\": false\n}",
